So sometimes crazy.

00:19:51.070 --> 00:19:51.430 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: Not certified.

00:19:51.430 --> 00:19:52.390 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: Exactly.

00:19:52.390 --> 00:19:55.570 align:middle line:84%
So it's good, but sometimes
crazy things come up,

00:19:55.570 --> 00:19:58.040 align:middle line:90%
and people just fall for it.

00:19:58.040 --> 00:20:01.990 align:middle line:84%
But then what happens is
that when we think of fear,

00:20:01.990 --> 00:20:04.370 align:middle line:90%
inquisition to start with.

00:20:04.370 --> 00:20:07.960 align:middle line:84%
And then you couldn't have
any of the sensitivity.

