00:40:34.230 --> 00:40:36.390 align:middle line:84%
and you position something
in this direction,

00:40:36.390 --> 00:40:37.680 align:middle line:90%
you create shadow.

00:40:37.680 --> 00:40:40.710 align:middle line:84%
But if we think
of light in a way

00:40:40.710 --> 00:40:45.690 align:middle line:84%
that one beam of light and you
turn other beam of light here,

00:40:45.690 --> 00:40:47.490 align:middle line:90%
it's just going to pass through.

00:40:47.490 --> 00:40:49.200 align:middle line:90%
We are talking about dimensions.

00:40:49.200 --> 00:40:51.900 align:middle line:84%
We are talking about
energies that they

00:40:51.900 --> 00:40:55.200 align:middle line:90%
are of different frequencies.

00:40:55.200 --> 00:40:59.440 align:middle line:84%
They belong to different layers
in this non-physical dimension.

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:02.730 align:middle line:84%
So I don't see how
the silver cord

00:41:02.730 --> 00:41:05.963 align:middle line:84%
could be severed with
everything I have witnessed.

00:41:05.963 --> 00:41:08.130 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: And it elongates
no matter how far you go.

00:41:08.130 --> 00:41:09.120 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: It elongates.

00:41:09.120 --> 00:41:11.670 align:middle line:84%
If people can have
experiences that they

00:41:11.670 --> 00:41:14.193 align:middle line:90%
went to other planets--

00:41:14.193 --> 00:41:15.360 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: In an astral body.

00:41:15.360 --> 00:41:16.485 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: In an astral body.

00:41:16.485 --> 00:41:19.260 align:middle line:84%
In a matter of sometimes
a couple of minutes,

00:41:19.260 --> 00:41:22.530 align:middle line:84%
and there are many accounts
like that, or seconds even.

00:41:22.530 --> 00:41:26.910 align:middle line:84%
So what would create a
problem to that silver cord?

00:41:26.910 --> 00:41:30.360 align:middle line:84%
The problem that
I do see is when

00:41:30.360 --> 00:41:32.730 align:middle line:84%
people are very
close to the body

00:41:32.730 --> 00:41:35.310 align:middle line:84%
and still not in full
control, and they

00:41:35.310 --> 00:41:39.040 align:middle line:84%
may be surprised by something
that may shock them, even

00:41:39.040 --> 00:41:39.840 align:middle line:90%
good things.

00:41:39.840 --> 00:41:41.423 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: And that
pulls them back in.

00:41:41.423 --> 00:41:43.165 align:middle line:84%
>>NANCI: That
pulls them back in.

00:41:43.165 --> 00:41:45.290 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: That's what
happened to me when I was 11.

00:41:45.290 --> 00:41:48.268 align:middle line:84%
It was that shock of
seeing my little body wham.

00:41:48.268 --> 00:41:50.560 align:middle line:84%
>>NANCI: And did you have
other experiences after this?

00:41:50.560 --> 00:41:50.870 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: Never.

00:41:50.870 --> 00:41:52.370 align:middle line:90%
I've never been able to do it.

00:41:52.370 --> 00:41:55.430 align:middle line:84%
>>NANCI: You are describing
exactly what so many people

00:41:55.430 --> 00:41:59.180 align:middle line:84%
have, because the
surprise, the shock--

00:41:59.180 --> 00:42:00.710 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: I've studied it.

00:42:00.710 --> 00:42:03.800 align:middle line:84%
I've interviewed people like
you who are the best at this.

00:42:03.800 --> 00:42:07.350 align:middle line:84%
But I've only done it the one
time, and it was by accident.

00:42:07.350 --> 00:42:08.150 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: Exactly.

00:42:08.150 --> 00:42:09.750 align:middle line:90%
And you could never forget that.

00:42:09.750 --> 00:42:12.030 align:middle line:84%
So we know it's not
the same of a dream.

00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:17.060 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is this surprise,
even of a good thing that

00:42:17.060 --> 00:42:19.160 align:middle line:84%
makes us come back
suddenly to the body

00:42:19.160 --> 00:42:22.250 align:middle line:84%
usually creates a mechanism
similar to the one

00:42:22.250 --> 00:42:23.600 align:middle line:90%
I created with my trauma.

00:42:23.600 --> 00:42:24.500 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: Let me ask you this--

00:42:24.500 --> 00:42:25.458 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: That holds us.

00:42:25.458 --> 00:42:27.770 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: When you're
going to bed, sometimes

00:42:27.770 --> 00:42:30.350 align:middle line:84%
right before you
fall asleep, you

00:42:30.350 --> 00:42:34.310 align:middle line:84%
feel a jarring effect, something
like something hits you.

00:42:34.310 --> 00:42:35.780 align:middle line:90%
And you wake up again.

00:42:35.780 --> 00:42:38.520 align:middle line:84%
Is that the astral
body starting to leave?

00:42:38.520 --> 00:42:39.320 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: Yes.

00:42:39.320 --> 00:42:43.290 align:middle line:84%
From what we have observed,
and in some cases witnessing

00:42:43.290 --> 00:42:47.700 align:middle line:84%
that when we are still awake,
yes, because we start relaxing.

00:42:47.700 --> 00:42:50.310 align:middle line:90%
These energies, they loosen up.

00:42:50.310 --> 00:42:53.130 align:middle line:84%
And then some parts of our
bodies or the whole body

00:42:53.130 --> 00:42:56.160 align:middle line:84%
just detach, and
we are surprised,

00:42:56.160 --> 00:42:57.390 align:middle line:90%
we are not expecting.

00:42:57.390 --> 00:42:59.940 align:middle line:84%
We are still very much
connected to the physical body.

00:42:59.940 --> 00:43:03.360 align:middle line:84%
And then you have a jerk,
which is the same process

00:43:03.360 --> 00:43:05.640 align:middle line:90%
of the sleep paralysis.

00:43:05.640 --> 00:43:06.600 align:middle line:90%
>>GEORGE: Same thing.

00:43:06.600 --> 00:43:07.975 align:middle line:84%
>>NANCI: Yes, we
start detaching.

00:43:07.975 --> 00:43:10.650 align:middle line:84%
You are just slightly
out, but you are not out.

00:43:10.650 --> 00:43:14.070 align:middle line:84%
And then you still in
the same perspective

00:43:14.070 --> 00:43:17.400 align:middle line:84%
of the physical body here,
still perceiving reality

00:43:17.400 --> 00:43:20.200 align:middle line:84%
from this area, but you are
not fully inside the body.

00:43:20.200 --> 00:43:22.410 align:middle line:84%
So you try to move, you
try to control your body,

00:43:22.410 --> 00:43:24.160 align:middle line:90%
and you can't.

00:43:24.160 --> 00:43:27.400 align:middle line:84%
And some people feel very
afraid, very trapped.

00:43:27.400 --> 00:43:29.590 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes some
entities take advantage

00:43:29.590 --> 00:43:31.540 align:middle line:90%
to make them even more afraid.

00:43:31.540 --> 00:43:34.870 align:middle line:84%
But never heard of
anyone having a problem

00:43:34.870 --> 00:43:38.500 align:middle line:84%
during sleep paralysis that
was like a permanent problem

00:43:38.500 --> 00:43:39.580 align:middle line:90%
or serious things.

00:43:39.580 --> 00:43:41.530 align:middle line:90%
It's more of being afraid.

00:43:41.530 --> 00:43:44.170 align:middle line:84%
But there are so many sensations
that happen at that moment.

00:43:44.170 --> 00:43:45.220 align:middle line:90%
The jerk awake.

00:43:45.220 --> 00:43:46.720 align:middle line:90%
Sensations of vibration.

00:43:46.720 --> 00:43:50.380 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes rocking, swinging,
feeling very light,

00:43:50.380 --> 00:43:52.210 align:middle line:90%
feeling very heavy.

00:43:52.210 --> 00:43:54.310 align:middle line:90%
Also same process.

00:43:54.310 --> 00:43:56.270 align:middle line:90%
Sensation of falling.

00:43:56.270 --> 00:44:00.790 align:middle line:84%
So many different sensations
we may experience.

00:44:00.790 --> 00:44:03.410 align:middle line:84%
But we do not know
how to make sense of--

00:44:03.410 --> 00:44:05.770 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: Do you ever
travel in your astral body

00:44:05.770 --> 00:44:09.050 align:middle line:90%
to escape reality?

00:44:09.050 --> 00:44:09.850 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: No.

00:44:09.850 --> 00:44:10.450 align:middle line:90%
Not really.

00:44:10.450 --> 00:44:11.440 align:middle line:84%
>>GEORGE: You've never
tried to get away.

00:44:11.440 --> 00:44:12.240 align:middle line:90%
>>NANCI: But no.

00:44:12.240 --> 00:44:14.320 align:middle line:90%
