00:44:24.470 --> 00:44:25.940 align:middle line:90%
There are many types.

00:44:25.940 --> 00:44:31.610 align:middle line:84%
But we can have certain types
in which it's just being

00:44:31.610 --> 00:44:35.010 align:middle line:90%
